savage, Julia.

102
00:05:10,744 --> 00:05:12,804
Look, I know you're
basically stoned on sugar,

103
00:05:12,879 --> 00:05:14,711
but if you could just
dial down the chipper.

104
00:05:14,815 --> 00:05:18,252
All I do is accept
what you fight.

105
