of curse on the castle?

117
00:05:51,918 --> 00:05:52,918
Did I?

118
00:05:54,588 --> 00:05:55,886
<i>It was so long ago.</i>

119
00:05:57,090 --> 00:05:58,251
<i>I hardly remember.</i>

