124
00:06:22,048 --> 00:06:24,517
<i>I believe I did work
up a little welcome.</i>

125
00:06:25,619 --> 00:06:29,317
Yes, since Ember made it
impossible for me to retake the throne,

126
00:06:29,389 --> 00:06:31,483
